request.description:
### 📊 Generate AI Video Report

Creates comprehensive AI analysis report for a specific video.

#### 📤 Response (200 OK)
```json
{
  "report": {
    "videoId": "video123",
    "sentimentScore": 0.85,
    "overallSummary": "Audience response is overwhelmingly positive...",
    "strengths": [
      "Clear explanation",
      "Good pacing",
      "High engagement"
    ],
    "improvements": [
      "Better lighting",
      "Longer duration"
    ],
    "nextVideoIdea": "Deep dive into advanced topics",
    "audienceFeedback": {
      "mostPositive": "Great tutorial!",
      "mostCritical": "Audio quality could be better",
      "commonQuestions": ["Can you make a follow-up?"]
    },
    "engagementMetrics": {
      "sentimentBreakdown": {
        "positive": 0.75,
        "neutral": 0.20,
        "negative": 0.05
      },
      "topKeywords": ["helpful", "clear", "tutorial", "learned"],
      "engagementTrend": "increasing"
    }
  }
}
```

#### 🔒 Authentication Required
- JWT token required
- YouTube channel must be connected

