request.description:
### 💬 Generate Smart Replies

Creates AI-powered, contextual responses to comments.

#### ✅ Request Body
```json
{
  "comments": [
    {
      "id": "string",
      "text": "string",
      "author": "string"
    }
  ]
}
```

#### 📤 Response (200 OK)
```json
{
  "replies": {
    "comment123": {
      "reply": "Thanks for the suggestion! I'm actually working on a React tutorial - coming soon! 🚀",
      "intent": "request",
      "emoji": "🚀",
      "priority": "high",
      "confidence": 0.92
    },
    "comment456": {
      "reply": "You're very welcome! So glad it helped you understand the concept better! 🎉",
      "intent": "gratitude",
      "emoji": "🎉",
      "priority": "medium",
      "confidence": 0.88
    }
  },
  "metadata": {
    "totalProcessed": 2,
    "avgConfidence": 0.9,
    "processingTime": "1.2s"
  }
}
```

#### 🔒 Authentication Required
- JWT token required

